node.text:
Feeling overwhelmingly honoured to have been asked to be the voice of ‘Mum’ in the new @catsprotection Christmas campaign... Based on the true story of one family and their little cat Casper ... such a magical and sweet tale reminding us of how important it is to microchip your pet... #MakeChristmasMagical and join us on #CaspersMagicalJourney.
Find out more and donate at www.cats.org.uk/caspers-Christmas ... Thank you 🐱

node.text: When I found out @GarnierUK were launching Reusable Eco Pads I couldn't wait to try them as anything that will help me reduce waste in my daily routine without compromising on ease is a win for me. I use them with Garnier’s Micellar Water to remove my makeup and cleanse my skin, and they’re honestly SO soft!! Each Pad can be re-used up to 1,000x times too... simple changes, big difference. Xxx 💚 #ad
